 TWICE凭借《With YOU-th》首次登上Billboard 200榜首https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-top-billboard-200-first-time-with-you-th-3596184?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=twice-top-billboard-200-first-与你共度的时光Carmen ChinMon, 04 Mar 2024 06:39:11 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3596184 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="两次荣登Youth Billboard 200第一名" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她们是第三个做到这一点的韩国流行女团</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-top-billboard-200-first-time-with-you-th-3596184">TWICE凭借《With YOU-th》首次登上公告牌200强，并</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="两次荣登Youth Billboard 200第一名" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/twice-with-you-th-billboard-200-number-one-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/twice">TWICE</a>凭借最新迷你专辑《With YOU-th》首次登上 Billboard 200 排行榜第一名。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/twice-with-you-th-review-3593527">TWICE – “With YOU-th”评论：欣喜地展示了他们的持久力</a></strong></li></ul><p>《With YOU&#39;th》于 2 月 23 日发行，在截至 2 月 29 日的一周内首次登上 Billboard 200 榜首，在美国售出了 95,000 张同等专辑单位。 <em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/twice-with-with-you-th-number-one-debut-billboard-200-albums-chart-1235620779/">Billboard</a></em>于昨天（3 月 3 日）宣布了这一壮举。</p><p>仅实体专辑销量和数字专辑下载量就达到了 90,000 张，创下了今年迄今为止韩国流行乐队首周销量的最高纪录。</p><p>尽管这标志着这九张专辑在他们的职业生涯中第五次进入排行榜前十名，但《With YOU-th》破纪录的销量使其成为他们第一张登上排行榜榜首的专辑。</p><p>借此，TWICE 现已成为继<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">BTS</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/superm">SuperM</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stray-kids">Stray Kids</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tomorrow-x-together">Tomorrow X Together</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ateez">ATEEZ</a>等之后第八个登上 Billboard 200 榜首的韩国流行音乐组合。值得注意的是，她们是韩国流行音乐历史上第三个实现这一壮举的女子组合。</p><p> Billboard 200 每周都会对美国最受欢迎的专辑进行排名，这是根据传统专辑销量、流媒体当量和数字歌曲下载当量的组合来确定的。</p><p> 《With YOU-th》的主打歌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-one-spark-music-video-3591752">《One Spark》的音乐录影带于上个月末与专辑同时发行</a>。该唱片还包含<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-i-got-you-remix-lauv-3582342">预发行单曲“I Got You”</a> ，该单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-i-got-you-remix-lauv-3582342">于 2 月 5 日获得了 Lauv 混音版</a>。</p><p> 《With YOU-th》是 TWICE 自 2023 年 3 月发行以主打歌《Set Me Free》为主打的《Ready To Be》以来近一年来首次以团体形式创作音乐。在 2023 年剩下的时间里，这个女团<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-ready-to-be-world-tour-dates-tickets-3402218">开始了大规模的 Ready To Be 世界巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-top-billboard-200-first-time-with-you-th-3596184">TWICE凭借《With YOU-th》首次登上公告牌200强，并</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
